import { Route, Routes } from "react-router-dom"
import { Home } from "./home"
import { Login } from "./login"
import { Nav } from "./nav"
import { Func } from "./function"

export const Routing=()=>{
    return <Routes>
        <Route path="mhome" element={<Home></Home>} ></Route>
        <Route path="mlogin" element={<Login></Login>} ></Route>
        <Route path="mfunction" element={<Func></Func>} ></Route>
        <Route path="mnav" element={<Nav></Nav>} ></Route>
       
    </Routes>
}
